.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: fuchsia, aquamarine, pink, purple, mauve
There are 5 different nationalities: malaysian, italian, mexican, colombian, german
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, oliveros, davidoff, bongani, alhambra
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, hot-chocolate, juice, 7up
5 different pets are kept: fish, snake, ferret, bird, lizard

1. the malaysian is the person who likes fuchsia
2. the italian is the owner of the fish
3. the person drinking fanta is the person who likes aquamarine
4. the mexican is the person drinking sprite
5. the person who likes aquamarine is to the right of the person who likes pink
6. the ritmeester-smoker is the owner of the lizard
7. the oliveros-smoker is the person who likes purple
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle
9. the colombian is on the far left
10. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the snake
11. the oliveros-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the bird
12. the bongani-smoker is the person drinking juice
13. the german is the alhambra-smoker
14. the colombian is to the left or right of the person who likes mauve

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   colombian	|    mexican	|     malaysian	|    italian	|    german	|
| Color		|    purple	|      mauve	|      fuchsia	|     pink	|     aquamarine	|
| Beverage	|     7up	|      sprite	|      hot-chocolate	| juice	|     fanta	|
| Cigar		|     oliveros	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| bongani	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     snake	|     bird	|     lizard	|     fish	|     ferret	|
